#hm-note[
  *Year Two Month 11 — Lead:* Students acquire small lead specimens (fishing weights or lead sheet) for metal meditation practice. Cold-only handling; nitrile gloves required for every contact. Lead storage in a sealed, labelled container away from food and living areas. No additional equipment beyond what is already listed is required.
]

